Title: The BEST LTM in Apex Legends History!
Description: The BEST LTM in Apex Legends History. Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks. Apex Easter Eggs. Apex Legends Nostalgia.  DUMMIEs Big Day LTM released in Apex Legends in Season 3 during the Grand Soiree Arcade Event. Within the Grand Soiree Collection Event, 7 LTMS were released, including Gold Rush Duos, Third-Person Mode, Always Be Closing, DUMMIEs Big Day, and After Dark regular battle royale modes for both Worldâ€™s Edge and Kingâ€™s Canyon.  Within the DUMMIE's Big Day game mode, every player was a DUMMIE and had the same abilities.  The DUMMIEs Tactical spawned a random piece of loot for you or your teammate.  The DUMMIEs had 3 Ultimate Abilities: Emergency Loot Pinata, Emergency Dance Party (which is now Mirage's Ultimate), and Emergency Area Heal. Title: What If Apex Legends Had 1st Person Finishers?
Description: What If Apex Legends Had 1st Person Finishers? Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks. Apex Legends Mods.  Performing Finishers in Apex Legends is a quick way to get back your Shields and to increase your EVO amount, but what if Finishers within Apex Legends were in 1st Person view rather than the normal 3rd Person view?  With the power of R5 Reloaded, a modded version of Apex Legends, we can see 1st Person Finishers for Legends such as Lifeline, Caustic, Mirage, and Loba! Description: EVERY Animation for Octane's Heirloom Recolor in Season 20 of Apex Legends. Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks.  Octane's Heirloom Recolor known as "Octane's Prototype" will be releasing in Season 20 of Apex Legends in the Inner Beast Collection Event. Octane's NEW Heirloom Recolor will have a Mythic Finisher, Mythic Banner Frame, and new inspect animations.  24 limited-time skins and cosmetics will be releasing during the Inner Beast Collection Event.  Within the Inner Beast Collection Event will be a new game mode known as "The Hunt" which will act similar to Hide and Seek!
